| Also Known As | {{ host.hostname_aliases|join(", ") }} |
{% endif -%}
| OS | {{ host.os or "N/A" }} |
| Tags | {{ mitre_tags }} |

{% if host.av_products %}
## Security Products
| Product | Status |
| --- | --- |
{% for product in host.av_products -%}
| {{ product }} | Detected |
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}
## Open Ports
| Port | Protocol | Service | Version | State |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
{% for port in host.ports -%}
| {{ port.number }} | {{ port.protocol }} | {{ port.service }} | {{ port.version or "N/A" }} | {{ port.state }} |
{% else -%}
| N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A |
{% endfor %}

## MITRE ATT&CK Mapping
| TTP | Name | Tactic | Source | Confidence |
| --- | ---- | ------ | ------ | ---------- |
{% for match in host.mitre_matches -%}
| {{ match.technique_id }} | {{ match.technique_name }} | {{ match.tactic }} | {{ match.source }} | {{ "%.0f%%" | format(match.confidence * 100) }} |
{% else -%}
| N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A |
{% endfor %}

## Severity
**Score:** {{ host.severity.value | title }}
**Reason:** {{ severity_reason }}

## Suggested Next Steps
